data.description: Welcome to this beautiful neutral open concept home.  Gently lived in for just a year and we need to relocate.  Bedrooms up have been repainted warm and neutral. Carpet removed at entry and replaced with beautiful large tile. Stairs and bedrooms up replaced as well.Open home w/bright lighting, purposeful placement of seating & appliances. MOVIE NIGHT in media room YES PLEASE! Historical Tomball TX. Well manicured surroundings and neighborhood ongoings. Pet friendly pond/walk path area minutes from your door.  Elementary in walking or bike riding distance. Quaint walkable downtown cafes, shops and live events from music to charity and family fun festivals! Access Grand Pkwy/Gosling, Mins from Woodlands Medical Center/multi-tiered facilities/MD Anderson Cancer, Memorial Hermann,Texas Children's Enjoy, Woodlands concerts in the Park. Mins to Woodlands, IAH,EXXON Mobil & Energy Corridor. Nearby gyms & Sports Complexes, competitive dive training/biking/nature trails all in a short drive.
